---
// Franchise band: off-white intro card + photo + animated "Seja um franqueado" card
---

<section class="bg-wevol-black py-24">
  <div class="wv-container grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="flex min-h-[400px] flex-col justify-center rounded bg-wevol-off-white p-3 xl:h-[500px]">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 px-6 py-2">
        <h2 class="wv-title text-[clamp(36px,3.13vw,60px)] text-wevol-ink" data-reveal="words">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-5">
            Leve a
            <img
              src="icons/wevol-logo-dark.svg"
              alt="WEVOL"
              class="h-[0.8em] w-auto translate-y-[0.05em]"
            />
          </span>
          <span class="mt-1 block">para sua cidade.</span>
        </h2>
        <p
          class="wv-title mt-2 max-w-[456px] text-[clamp(16px,1.05vw,20px)] leading-[1.25] tracking-[-0.02em] text-wevol-ink"
          data-reveal="lines"
        >
          Conheça a oportunidade de fazer parte da expansão de uma marca que está transformando
          saúde, performance e longevidade.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <img
      src="images/franquia.png"
      alt="Treino com tecnologia WEVOL"
      class="h-[400px] w-full rounded object-cover xl:h-[500px]"
      data-reveal-img
    />

    <a
      href="#"
      class="group relative flex min-h-[400px] flex-col items-end justify-between overflow-hidden rounded bg-gradient-to-l from-wevol-grad-1 to-wevol-grad-2 p-6 focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-wevol-orange xl:h-[500px]"
      data-franquia-cta
    >
      {/* hover: gradient fades into solid WEVOL Orange */}
      <span
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-wevol-orange opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500 ease-out group-hover:opacity-100"
        aria-hidden="true"
      ></span>

      <span class="relative block size-20 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
        {/* arrow exits top-right, twin re-enters from bottom-left */}
        <img
          src="icons/franquia-arrow.svg"
          alt=""
          class="absolute inset-0 size-20 transition-transform duration-500 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)] group-hover:translate-x-[110%] group-hover:translate-y-[-110%]"
        />
        <img
          src="icons/franquia-arrow.svg"
          alt=""
          class="absolute inset-0 size-20 translate-x-[-110%] translate-y-[110%] transition-transform duration-500 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1)] group-hover:translate-x-0 group-hover:translate-y-0"
        />
      </span>

      <span
        class="wv-title relative w-full text-right text-[clamp(44px,3.75vw,72px)] leading-none text-wevol-ink transition-colors duration-500 group-hover:text-wevol-off-white"
      >
        Seja um franqueado
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
